instruction: Generate a poem given a subject.
output:
Puppies, so small and so sweet 
Living in fur, so soft and light 
Playing around in the sun
Eyes bright and noses wet
Bouncing off with no goal in sight
Frolicking with so much delight 
It's hard not to smile watching their show
Cuddling up with no cares to know. 
Ah, those precious little bundles of joy,
Coloring our days with so much delight.
